erver/interact/26903/', '', 'Clopidogrel, Cilostazol, Lepirudin, Acenocoumarol, Urokinase, Dipyridamole, Warfarin, Argatroban, Desirudin, Eptifibatide, Streptokinase, More', '', 1767369485);
